Uses of Package
org.commonvox.insight.anomaly_detector

  • Classes in org.commonvox.insight.anomaly_detector used by org.commonvox.insight.anomaly_detector 
    Class and Description
    PurchaseManager
    An instance of the PurchaseManager class serves as the container for recent purchases of either a User or a network of Users, up to the capacity established by the purchase threshold.
    PurchaseManager.PurchaseKey
    Provides unique key for purchase transactions, since timestamps themselves are not necessarily unique.
    User
    An instance of the User class serves as the container for friends and recent purchases of a user, and the User class crucially provides the #getAnomalyData method, which invokes anomaly-detection on each of a user's new purchases.
